recEcsMotor.c
	Added #define GEN_SIZE_OFFSET and #undef GEN_SIZE_OFFSET bracketing
	the include of ecsMotorRecord.h. This is a standard technique to
	get the ecsMotorRecordSizeOffset routine inserted automatically
	from ecsMotorRecord.h, which in turn is generated from the record
	dbd file (PG 25/Mar/02).

recEcsMotor.c
