	dbCaAddOutlink since they are no longer required in the GEM7
	release (PG 25/Mar/02).

recEcsMotor.c
	Changed calls to recGblGetFastLink() to dbGetLink(). Note: This
	was done incorrectly the first time since the calling sequence was
	wrong. Andy Foster found the problem and fixed it (PG 25/Mar/02).

recEcsMotor.c
	Changed abs() calls to fabs() (PG 25/Mar/02).

recEcsMotor.c
	Changed reference to pmr->dol.value.value in initLinks with a
	call to recGblInitConstantLink() (PG 25/Mar/02).
	
drvAbDf1.c
drvSerial.c
	The AB and the serial driver both report warnings when compiled.
	The problem originates in the bad practice of using the return
	value of a pointer value as a logical expression. This was not
	changed for now (PG 25/Mar/02).

alh/Makefile.Host
	Changed TOP to ecs (PG 27/Mar/02).

alh/ecs.alhConfig -> ecs.alh
