capfast/shuttersStatus.sch
	The old record used to display the skew encoder value will be
	now used to display the skew value in millimiters. The PLC
	program was changed accordingly. The record was renamed and
	a calculation record was added to deal with the case of negative
	skew values (PG 12/Nov/02).

