------------------------------------+------------------------------------
				 V2-2
			   Vent gate currents
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

ecsInitCP.pv
	Changed the top and bottom shutter park position (PG 16/Dec/02).

capfast/ventcurr.sch
capfast/ventcurr.sym
capfast/misc.sch
	Added vent gate drive current interface to the database. The drive
	currents and read from the PLC from words 49 to 56 as follows:

		N11:49  East Vent Gate drive 4X
		N11:50  East Vent Gate drive 4Y
		N11:51  East Vent Gate drive 4Z
		N11:52  East Vent Gate drive 4W

		N11:53  West Vent Gate drive 5X
		N11:54  West Vent Gate drive 5Y
		N11:55  West Vent Gate drive 5Z
		N11:56  West Vent Gate drive 5W

	the drive currents are sent in tenths of Amper (PG 19/Dec/02).

capfast/domecurr.sch
	Modified naming convention of dome drive current records to match
	the conventions introduced in the vent gates (PG 19/Dec/02).

capfast/ecs.sch
	Added word definitions for the vent gate current words: evg4x,
	evg4y, evg4z, evg4w, wvg5x, wvg5y, wvg5z and wvg5w. The dome
	drive current words were renamed dmg4x, dmg4y, dmg4z, dmg4w, dmg4e,
	dmg4e, dmg4g and dmg4h (19/Dec/02).

adl/status.adl
adl/ventcurr.adl
adl/na.adl
	Added new screen for vent gate currents. The menu was updated
	in the status window for the dome and vent gate currents. The
	menu also contains the hooks for the shutter currents, currently
	pointing to the "not available" screen (PG 19/Dec/02).

